file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: '<font size="2" color="red">MIT License</font>'
  title: Calculate-Distance-Matrix
  contact:
    name: Erlan Lucio
    url: https://github.com/lucioerlan
  version: '1.0'
servers:
- url: http://localhost:5000/api
  variables: {}
paths:
  /get-files:
    get:
      tags:
      - Routes
      summary: RETURN DOCS
      operationId: RETURNDOCS
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /process-files:
    post:
      tags:
      - Routes
      summary: CREATE DOC
      operationId: CREATEDOC
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            encoding: {}
            schema:
              required:
              - fullname
              - chooseDistances
              - docFile
              type: object
              properties:
                fullname:
                  type: string
                  example: routes
                chooseDistances:
                  type: string
                  example: distance.text
                docFile:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
        required: false
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
tags:
- name: Routes
  description: ''
